verses.lines:
Gw'oli Mutukuvu, Ayinza byonna!
Emirimu gyo gitenda erinnya lyo;
Gw'oli Mutukuvu, W'akisa wa maanyi;
Katond(a) omu, Ali mu busatu.

Tusinza nnyo erinya lye (O)mulokozi waffe;
Awamu n'abantu~ bo~nna, Kabaka waffe Yesu;
Awamu n'abantu~ bo~nna, Kabaka wa~ffe Yesu.

Abant(u) abaasonyiyibwa olw'ekisa kye Ye,
Mumufukaamiri~re~nga, Kabaka wafe Yesu;
Mumufukaamiri~re~nga, Kabaka wa~ffe Yesu.

Amawanga gonn(a) ag'ensi, Mujje eri Yesu;
Tumuw(e) ekitiibwa~ kyo~nna, Kabaka waffe Yesu;
Tumuw(e) ekitiibwa~ kyo~nna, Kabaka wa~ffe Yesu.

(A)wamu ne bamalayika, Ffe tulimusinza,
Okumweyanza bu~li~jjo, Kabaka waffe Yesu;
Okumweyanza bu~li~jjo, Kabaka wa~ffe Yesu.

Siyinza kugenda~ nzekka
Kibuyaga mungi~ ddala;
Emitengo gya Se~tani
Era n'ama~gye ge gonna;
Nsaba Ggwe obima~lewo,
Kale~ ka ntambule naawe.

Bwe mbeera awamu~ naawe,
Essanyu ly'ensi si~ kintu;
Ka ntambule n'obu~zira,
Nga nkutte e~bendera yo;
Olintuusa mu Sa~yuni,
Nga nta~mbula wamu naawe.

Katonda~ tu~siibule~ nno, Kkiriz(a) e~tte~ndo lyaffe;
Sonyiwa~ bo~nn(a) abeene~nya, Balyoke~ ba~lokoke
Tu~le~menga, tu~le~menga, O~ku~nyi~za (O)~mwoyo gwo.

Otubee~re~ tuleme~nga, Okwesa~nyu~sa ffekka;
Tukuza~ e~ssanyu lya~ffe, Mu kuwu~mmu~la kwaffe;
Naa~w~e beera, naa~we~ beera, (E)ssa~nyu~ li~ngi~ gye tuli.

Ayi Kita~ffe~ obakuu~me, Abata~li~dda nate;
(E)biro bya~bw(e) e~by'okusi~ga, Bireet(e) o~ku~kungula
A~ba~lidda, a~ba~lidda, Ba~ko~le~nga~ n'amanyi.

Omuki~sa~ gwa Kita~ffe N'ogw'Omwa~na~ we Yesu;
N'ogw'Omwo~yo~ (O)mutuku~vu, Gukke ku~ myo~yo gyaffe
Tu~be~nga wamu~ n'e~ssanyu, N'e~mi~re~mbe,~ Amiina.

Ontegeeze ku bya Yesu, Mbinywereze ku mwoyo;
Ebyo bising(a) obulungi Byonn(a) eby'omunsi muno,
Bamalayika baayimba Yesu bwe yazaalibwa;
Katond(a) aweebwe (e)kitibwa, (E)mirembe gi~be mu nsi.~

Bwe yabeera mu lukoola, Mu nnaku ezo zonna;
Bwe yakemebwa Setaani, Era bwe yawangula,
Mbulir(a) eby'omulimu gwe, N'ebyennaku ze zonna;
Bwe yabonyabonyezebwa N'anyomebwa~ abantu.~

Nsanyuse, nsanyuse; Yesu yannazaak(o) ebibi;
Y(e) anjagaza by'ayagala; Ansanyus(a) ennaku zonna;
Nsanyuse, nsanyuse, Yesu yannazaak(o) ebibi.

(O)kwagala kwo Ggwe Mu~kama, Kusing(a) essanyu lyo~nna;
Wekolere mu ff(e) e~weema (O)tufukek(o) ekisa~ kyo.
Ggwe kwagal(a) okulo~ngofu, Yesu Ggw(e) Omusaasi~zi;
(O)bulokozi tubwe~taaga, Wony(a) obunafu bwa~ffe.

Ye amanyi (o)buzibu bwaffe,
Alitutuusa mu ddembe;
Tewali mukwano nga Mukama;
Tewali, tewali.

Mukama Ggwe eyantonda, Ndi wuwo okuv(a) edda;
Ettabaza yo gye wampa, Eyakenga bulijjo;
Mu maka agekitiibwa, Gewannongooseza nze,
Ndigenda nga njijudde nnyo, Essanyu mu mutima.

Yesu ompe omukisa, Nga nkyali mu maaso go;
Ntunulira n'ekisa kyo, Ondage amaaso go.
Ompe omutima gwo Ggwe, Mbe mutukuvu nga Ggwe;
Neerage nga ndi mwana wo, Ggw(e) ampa obutukuvu.

Nzuddeyo ow'Omukwano, Yaf(a) okundokola nze,
Kubanga obu~lamu bwe, Ye bwe yagabira nze;
Nze sirina kya bugagga, Ebyange bibye byonna;
Nneewaayo mu mi~kono gye, Mukwano gwange ddala.

Nzuddeyo ow'Omukwano, Yaweebw(a) amaanyi mangi;
Ge galintuusa~ ewuwe; Sitya balabe bonna.
Eby'eggulu mbirengera, Bimyansa nnyo nga ffeeza;
Nze kankole, nfu~be, nwane! Alidd(a) okumpummuza.

Nzuddeyo ow'Omukwano, Mulungi ow'ekisa;
Angabira ku~ maanyi ge, Annu'gamy(a) er(a) andiisa
Ebiriwo n'ebirijja, Tebirinjawukanya;
(E)mirembe egi~taggwawo, Yesu mukwano gwange.

Nsanyuk(a) okubinyu~mya, Bya kitalo~ ddala;
Nabinyumyanga ebyo Bye~ tulowoo~zako;
Nabinyumyanga ebyo Bikulu nnyo gye~ndi;
N'olw'ekyo nsanyuka nnyo, (O)kubyogera wonna.

Yesu Mukama wange, Nesig(a) amaanyi go;
Sitya balabe bange, Ne bwe bannumba;
Onkuum(a) ennyo lwa ki~sa, Siriko kye ntidde
Mu ngalo za Kitange Mwe mpummulira.

Setaani bw'ab(a) annumba N'ettima lye lingi;
Buli lw'ajj(a) okunnimba, Nziramu bwe nti,
"Vaawo genda~ Setaani, Yesu yakusinga;
Nali nkusenze edda, Ne nkusenguka".

Ka 'ngumirenga ku Yesu
Byonn(a) eby'ensi butaliimu;
Byonn(a) eby'ensi butaliimu.

Ff(e) abagala~ Yesu Ka tulage (e)~ssanyu!
Leka tuyimb(e) oluyimba, Leka tuyimb(e) oluyimba;
Kuba tusanyuse, Kuba tusanyuse.

Musirike~ mwenna Abatatya~ Yesu;
Naye abaana ba Yesu, Naye abaana ba Yesu,
Tuyimbe n'essanyu, Tuyimbe n'essanyu.

Ensi yaffe esembera, Ey'emirembe (e)nnungi;
Eri kumpi nga nnungi nnyo! Tunatuulanga omwo.
Wulira ennyimb(a) ennungi, Ziwulirwa mu bbanga~;
Abantu bangi bayimba, 'Tunater(a) okutuuka.'

Okukkiriza kwe nsaba Kwekweraga ennyo;
Ebikemo nga byetala Neme kutya n'okubuusabuu~sa,
N'oku~~buu~sabuusa.

Ensi nga ekambuwadde, Nze mbe nga sifaayo;
Obanga bansekerera, Kiremenga kuzigya ku Ye~su,
Mbeere~~ nga~ ku Yesu.

Mukama mp(a) okukkiriza, Okutaddirira;
Byonna ebirimberako Bimpanguze ontuus(e) eyo gy'~oli,
Ontuu~~s(e) eyo gy'~oli.

Beera nange obudde buzibye;
Enzikiza ekwata: beera nange;
Sirina nze mubeezi mulala,
Gwabeera abanaku, nange, mbeera!

Nkwetaga Ggwe emisana nekiro;
Setani kyatya kubeerawo kwo;
Katonda wange, Ebire bwe bijja,
Omusana bwe gwaka, beera nange!

Mujje mwenna abakooye, Nokutegana kwensi,
Yesu ye anaabaniiriza, Nokusaasira okungi;
Mujje mwenna, Mujje mwenna, Abayita temutya.

Temutya newakubadde, Ngebibi byammwe bingi;
Kyabakuutira kye kino; Mwenenye abasonyiwe;
Omwoyo gwe, Omwoyo gwe, Ye anabatukuza.

Laba Omwana wa Katonda, Leero abawolereza!
Munaawo na lwa musaayi, Bwe mwesigira ddala;
Ekisa kye, Ekisa kye, Ekirokola bonna.

Abatukuvu be bonna, Bamusinza nessanyu,
Abomu nsi ne mu ggulu, Bayimba amatendo ge;
Aleruya! Aleruya! Yesu Omulokozi.

Wulira akuyita, Londa ye vva ku byensi,
Ali awo ku luggi, Anakuwa essanyu;
Olwerinya lye egganzi.

Yesu wange yangamba nti, "Kye nkuwa kya buwa;
Nywa amazzi agobulamu, Owone enyonta yo".
Ne nsembera awali Yesu, Ne nnywa amazzi ago;
Ne nfuna amaanyi mu mwoyo,
Kakano ndi wuwe.

Amakungula, Tegaalwewo;
Olunaku olwentiisa lujja!
Ssalawo, tolemwa, Gwe tobuusabuusa;
Kkiriza olwa leero, Ngakya yita.

Yesu atuyita fenna, Tukole mu nnimiro;
Kubanga zonna zengedde, Anakola aluwa?
Ayita ggwe era nange, Empeera ye nnene nnyo;
Ani addamu nessanyu, Nti "Nze nzuno, ontume".

Omubi oli yasanyuka Okulab a ensulo eyo;
Nange omwonoonyi ennyo, Nnaatukuzibwa omwo.
Nnaatukuzibwa omwo, Nnaatukuzibwa omwo;
Nange omwonoonyi ennyo, Nnaatukuzibwa omwo.

Ayi Omwana gwEndiga, Omusaayi gwo gukola;
Okutuusa ekkanisa yo, Lwelinunulibwa.
Lwelinunulibwa, Lwelinunulibwa;
Okutuusa ekkanisa yo, Lwelinunulibwa.

Okuva lwennalab a ensulo, Eyebiwundu byo;
Ndowooza ku kwagala kwo, Okutuusa lwe ndifa.
Okutuusa lwe ndifa, Okutuusa lwe ndifa;
Ndowooza ku kwagala kwo, Okutuusa lwe ndifa.

Nze omwonoonyi lukulwe, Yesu yafa ku lwange;
Yafa mbeere mu ggulu, Yafa nze nneme kufa;
Ngettabi ku zzabbibu, Ndi wuwe naye wange.

Okwagala kwe kungi nnyo, Kutuuka waggulu nnyo;
Era kukka wansi nnyo, Kwo kwa mirembe gyonna;
Yannoonya nanzuula nze, Nga sinnamukowoola!

Omwonoonyi lukulwe, Kristo ye byonna gyendi;
Amanyi byeneetaaga, Annumirwak o ennaku;
Nze bwemba naye sitya, Abeera ngabo yange.

Onyambe, Mukama, Olwokutegeera Ekigambo kyo;
Omwoyo wo annungamye Nange nnaasomanga,
Ndyoke nkutegeere Mu kitabo.

Wano ndi mu kabi Nolwekyo sembera Kumpi nange;
Onkwata ku mukono Nneme okukankana
Ontwale ewuwo, Ngokomyewo!

Omwana wa Katonda, Okomewo mangu nnyo;
Beera naffe! Tukole byosiima, Byoyagala byonna
Emiyembe gyonna, Tube babo.

Tukola lwa ssanyu, Naye si lwa nnaku;
Yesu alituwa empeera; Mu kufiirwa kwaffe,
Mu kulumwa okungi, Aba naffe bwetumwesiga.

Mukama, nze nnina ebibi, Naye ekisa kyo kingi;
Ompise okujja gyoli,
Nzomwonoonyi, Yesu nzijja.

Okwagala kwo okunene Nekisa kyo bimpaludde;
Kye njagala, kusenga Ggwe,
Nzomwonoonyi, Yesu nzijja.

Yesu, Omusana omulala, saagala,
Amaaso go galabika Gyendi nga enjuba;
Amadaala agagenda Mu ggulu ge gano;
Omusalaba gwo, Yesu, Era gwe gwange nze.

Ndi kumpi n'a~maka gaffe,
Kumpi nnyo, ku~mpi nnyo leero;
Nnaate~r(a) okutuuka.

Mu lugendo lwange lwonna, Yesu ankulembera;
Abalab(e) abalinnumba Ye alibawangula;
Era (a)lintuusa n'essanyu Lingi mu mirembe gye;
[Enjala bw'eba ng'ennuma Andiisa ku mmere ye.]x2

Mu lugendo lwange lwonna, Yesu onkulembera;
Ggwe Omulokozi wange Eyanfuul(a) omwana wo;
Ka nkutendereze bwentyo (E)miremb(e) egitaggwawo,
[Nayimba n'essanyu lingi, Ggwe Mununuzi wange.]x2

"Mwe munywerenga," Bweyasuubiza;
"Ndibawa eggulu n'ensi empya;
Era mulifuga wamu nange, Muliweebw(a) engule,
Mwe munywerenga."

Katutunule nga tusabanga,
Alijja mu ssaawa etamanyiddwa;
Tumanyi nga ali kumpi ddala;
Olw'obubonero bweyatuw(a) edda.

Tusanyuke Yesu ajja! Ens(i) emwanirize;
Buli~ o~mu~yetee~ge~ke~, N'ebitonde byo~nna
E~by'eggulu n'e~nsi, Byo~nna~ bimu~tendereze.

Yesu ajja okufuga! Fenna tuyimbe nnyo;
Enso~zi~ n'e~migga~ byo~nna~, Bimusanyuki~re,
Bi~mutendere~ze; Ka~ bi~yimbe~nga n'essanyu.

Ajja (o)kuleeta eddembe! Amawanga gonna;
Gali~ra~ba~ (e)kitii~bwa~ kye~, Nga gatendere~za,
E~ra gasanyu~ka, O~kwa~gala~ kwe okungi.

Lowooza ekisa ky(e) ekingi, N'omuwendo gwe yawaayo;
Yalek(a) ekitiibwa kye ggulu, N'ajja okufa ku lwaffe;
Ndowooza kimusanyusa nnyo, Ng'alaba beyanunula;
Nga beetegeker(a) okudda kwe, Nga balinda, batunula.

Bwe ndimal(a) omulimu ku nsi, Nentuuka gy'ali,
Era nga nnyambadd(e) ogw(o) ogutafa;
Ndi mutegeera Yesu, nga ntuuse emitala, Era n'essanyu alinnyaniriza.

Bwe ndiraba ku maaso ge ndibeera n'essanyu,
Ndimwebaza Olw'ekisa ky(e) ekingi;
Okusaasira kwa Katonda tekusingika, Atusanyiz(a) ebifo mu maka ge.

Ampe ekyambalo kye ekyeru ng'annyingiza,
N'antuusa eyo etali kukaaba;
Gye ndibeera n'ennyimba ez'essanyu bulijjo, Negomba nsooke nsisinkane Yesu.

Katond(a) alisangula, (A)maziga gaffe gonna;
Teri nnaku na kufa~, Era teri kiro.
(Eyo teri nnaku na kufa)

Okwagala we kuba tewaba nnaku;
Amaka ag'ekisa gajjul(a) essanyu;
Buli wantu nga ddembe,
Mboozi empomerevu,
Liba ssanyu jjerere, Mu maka gaffe.

Ne Yesu asanyuka, Nga twagalana,
Okukyaawa n'obuggya tebibeeerawo;
Maka agaagalana,
Gabeera ga muwendo;
Goolesa obulungi, Obwa Kitaffe.

Mmenyer(a) omugaati, Ayi Yesu,
Nga bwewakola ku lubalama;
Mu byawandiikibwa Nkunoonya Ggwe;
Kigamb(o) omulamu, Nze nkwetaaga.

W(a) amazima gano, Omukisa,
Nga bwewakola e Galiraaya;
Obusibe bwange Obukomye;
Obeere byonna mu byonna gyendi.

(E)bigambo byo Yesu, Bwe bulamu,
Njagal(a) okugonda naye nnemwa;
Gwe buyambi bwange, N'obulamu;
Bweng'onder(a) ekigambo mpangula.

(O)lwazi lw'edda n'edda Ggwe, Olwanjatikira nze;
Omwo mwe nekweka nze, (O)musaayi gwe mwe gwava;
Ebibi binziyeeko, Nfuula omuwanguzi.

Emirimu gy'engalo, N'okufuba kw'omuntu,
N'amazig(a), agajj(a) ennyo, Emisana n'ekiro;
Byo tebiggyawo bibi, Ggwe wekka (O)mulokozi.

Sirina nze bulungi, Nkwesize Ggwe bwesizi;
Omwereere nnyambaza, Omunaku mp(a) ekisa;
Laba bwendi omubi, Onaaze, nkuweereze.

Bwe ndituuka mu ggulu, Nga nnina ebibala;
Bwe ndiraba Ggwe Yesu, Ne nsanyukira w'oli:
Ndibeera nga siyinza, Okwegulumizanga.

(O)musingi gw'ekkanisa, Ye Yesu Mukama;
Kye kitonde ky(e) ekiggya, Mu mazzi n'Enjiri;
Ye yamuggya mu ggulu, Eb(e) Omugole we;
(O)musaayi gwagigula, Yafa ebe nnamu.

Eri mu buli ggwanga, Naye eri emu;
Mukama, (o)kukkiriza, (o)kubatiza kumu;
(E)rinnya limu lyesinza, Erya emmer(e) emu,
Erina essuubi limu, Okudda kwa Yesu.

Newakubadd(e) enyoomwa, Era n'esaasirwa;
Abalabe baayo ne bwebanagiyuuza;
Abakkiriza baayo, Tebajjulukuke;
Er(a) obudde tebuulwe, Bayimb(e) olw'essanyu.

Mu kubonaabon(a) ennyo, Mu kufuba kwayo;
Esuubir(a) emirembe, Egy'olubeerera;
(O)kutuusa lweriraba Ekyasuubizibwa,
Olw(o) erib(a) ewangudde, Er(a) eriwummula.

Wakisa, Era yatuzaala; Mwagazi, Tumufanane;
Tukola lwa kwagala, kutuwa amaanyi,
Kutuwa ekis(a) ekingi Er(i) abantu bonna.

Anjagala era mmwagala Ye;
Yakka mu ns(i) olw'okutufiirira;
(O)kwagala kwamuleeta ku muti,
Yesu atwagala ffe bwagazi.

Yesu yajja mu mutima -[gwange], Yesu yajja mu mutima -[gwange],
Nzijudd(e) essanyu lingi mu mwoyo gwange;
Okuva lwe yajja munze.

Mbe wuwo (Yesu), Mbe wuwo (Yesu);
Ekyo nze kyenkusaba,
Mbe wuwo (Yesu), Mbe wuwo (Yesu);
Mbe wuwo nzenna Yesu.

Ndyambal(a) engule ya zaabu mu ggulu;
Nditikkulw(a) omugugu nga ntuus(e) eka;
Ndyambazibw(a) ebyeru, Ndiyimb(a) oluyimba
Olw'obulokozi Nga ntuus(e) eka.

Wulir(a) ebigambo bya Yesu, Bya bulamu bya mazima;
Gw(e) ataty(a), atasaba, Wulira leero,
Ba mukis(a) abakwata ebyo.

Okuwulira nga tokola, (E)bisuubizo bye tofuna;
Okubiwulira kyokka tekiyamba,
Ba mukis(a) abakola ebyo.

Baliyingira mu kibuga, Teri kibi teri nnaku;
Nga batukuziddw(a) emirembe gyonna,
Balye ku muti (o)gw'obulamu.

Mukama nze nzize wooli n'obuyinike bungi;
Omutima gwange gukooye zuukuka ondokole;
Ebibi binnakuwazza, Bigenda kunzita
Omulokozi wange Mukama, Ggwe wekka ggwe nneesiga.

(O)bwesigwa bwo bungi, Ayi Kitaffe;
Ggwe tokyukakyuka lubeerera,
Okusaasirakwo tekuliremwa;
Ggwe waliwo era olibaawo!

Onsonyiw(a) ebibi, omp(a) emirembe;
Obaaw(o) onsanyusa onnung'amya,
Omp(a) amaanyi leero, n'essuub(i) ery'enkya;
(E)mikisa gyo gyange, n'abalala.

Twal(a) obu~la~mu bwange, Obutu~ku~ze bwo~nna;
Twal(a) emiko~no gyange~, Gikozese byo~ya~gala,
Gikole byo~yagala.

Twal(a) ebi~ge~re byange, Bitambu~le~ ku lu~lwo;
Twal(a) eddoboo~zi lyange~, Likuyimbire~ Ka~baka,
Likuyimbi~re wekka!

Twala na~ka~mwa kange, Kajjuz(e) o~bu~baka~bwo;
(E)bintu byange~ (e)by'omunsi~, Bikozese by'o~ya~gala,
Bikole byo~yagala.

Twal(a) ebyo~bye~njagala, Byonna bi~fuu~ke bi~byo;
Twal(a) omuti~ma gwange~, Ogufuule e~nte~be yo,
Entebe kwo~fugira.

Twal(a) okwa~ga~la kwange, Kwonna ku~bee~re kukwo;
Ntwala nzenna~ mbe wuwo~, Emiremb(e) egi~ta~ggwawo;
(E)miremb(e) egi~ta~ggwawo.

Oba waliwo ebigambo, By'oyagala njogere,
Oba waliw(o) ali mu kibi, Gw'oyagala nkomyewo;
Nga Ggwe mukule~mbeze wange, Ekkubo wadde~ nga bbi;
(O)bubaka bwo nze nnaabwoge~ranga, Njogere ky'oyagala.

Netaaga okuwulira Ku by'obulokozi~;
Nnyongere okubimanya (E)bigambo bya Yesu;
Bye biga~mbo ddala Eby'obu~loko-zi.

Mukama yekka atuwa (E)bigambo by'essanyu~;
Ebireeta omwonoonyi, Eri obulamu;
Mukama~ by'atuwa Bitutu~se gya-li.

Ebigambo bya Mukama, Mwe mul(i) obulamu~;
Era bituwa eddembe, N'amaanyi g'omwoyo;
Ebibi bi~gwawo, Mu linya~ lya Ye-su.

Muka – m(a) ali mu yekaalu~ ye;
Muka – m(a) ali mu yekaalu~ ye,
Ensi zonna zisinze,
Zonna zivunname mu maaso ge;
Sirika! Sirika!
Mu maaso ge;
A – mii – na!

Simanyi binambaako, Katond(a) abinkweka;
Nga ntambula ngenda mu maaso, Andaga e~bipya,
Era buli ssanyu lyampa, Kibeera kyewuunyo.

Ka mmu~gobererenga, Mmwesi~ge sityenga;
Buli ssaawa mmuyimbira, Ekyo akimanyi~
Buli ssaawa mmuyimbira,- - - Ekyo akimanyi.

Eby'okumpi byendaba, Byokka byenetaaga;
(O)musana gwe ggulu gwaka nnyo, Ng(a) eby'ensi bi~genze;
Era mmuwu~lir(a) ang'amba – "Ngoberera totya!"

Kirung(i) obutamanya, Kya mukisa gyendi;
Ankwata ku mukono gwange, Tayinza ku~ndeka,
Awummuz(a) o~mwoyo gwange, Er(a) anjagala nnyo!

N'olw'ekyo ng'enda naye, Sikola kirala;
Mu bizibu nga ndi ne Yesu, Kinsingir(a) e~ssanyu,
Ka mmukkiri~ze mmwesige, So si maaso gange.

Ku lunaku (o)lw'emirembe, Ka tuyimb(e) ekitiibwa kyo;
Olutujjukiza Yesu, Lweyatonda ensi zonna,
Yalutuwa okulega, Ku ssanyu ery'omu ggulu.

(E)nnyimba z'okutendereza, Ziwulirw(a) eyo mu ggulu;
Ba seraafi bakusinza, Bavunnama mu maaso go,
Ensi zonna tuyimbire, Yesu eyatonda byonna.

E-mi-kisa gyo, Yesu ffe gyetwetaaga;
(E)mikis(a) egy'okudd(a) obuggya,
Tusab(a) ogitwongere.

Ka tutambule, tumwolekere,
Tuteekwa okuwangu~la;
[E]ngabo, [e]bbendera, bimasemase;
Amazima ge tegalemwa.
